		<span style="color: #050505;">   <img src="http://www.chinacno.org/images/2012/12/yyt/25-poster.jpg" border="0" width="500" height="750" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /> </span>
 
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: x-large;"><strong>庆祝中乌建交二十周年音乐会——乌克兰音乐日</strong></span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2012</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">12</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">25</span>日晚<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">19:30</span></span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">地点：民族音乐厅</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: small;"><span style="font-size: medium;"> </span></span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 90px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">一、谢尔盖<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">·</span>拉赫玛尼诺夫第二交响曲</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">01. I</span>：广板<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">-</span>有节制的快板</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">02. II</span>：谐谑曲（很快的快板）</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">03. III</span>：柔板</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">04. </span>终乐章（活泼的快板）</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">05. </span>练声曲（作品号<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">34</span>之<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">14</span>）</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">06. </span>间奏曲（选自歌剧《阿列科》）</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">07. </span>妇女的舞蹈（选自歌剧《阿列科》）</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 90px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 90px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 90px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">二、<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Overture to opera “Taras Bulba”  </span></span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">序曲选自歌剧片段《达拉斯·布尔巴》</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">作曲：米科拉·里森科（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Mikola Lysenko</span>）</span></p>
<p class="Section1"><span style="color: #050505;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;"> </span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;"> </span></span></p>
<p class="Section1"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: small;"> </span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square;">
<li>
<div class="Section1"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: large;"><strong>乌克兰国家爱乐乐团简介</strong></span></div>
</li>
</ul>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: small;"><img src="http://www.chinacno.org/images/2012/12/yyt/Ukraine/ukraine-logo.jpg" border="0" width="181" height="169" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /><br /><br /><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">乌克兰国家爱乐乐团</span></strong></span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: medium;"><a href="http://uaphil.org/?lang=en" title="Symphony Orchestra of National Philharmonic of Ukraine"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Symphony Orchestra of National Philharmonic of Ukraine</span></a></span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">        <br /> <img src="http://www.chinacno.org/images/2012/12/yyt/Ukraine/uk-00.png" border="0" width="635" height="354" /></span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: medium;">  </span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">乌克兰国家爱乐乐团，成立于苏联解体后的<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1995</span>年，根据其时乌克兰总统库奇马的要求，汇集了前苏联乌克兰籍的音乐精英们成立的国家级交响乐团。常驻有<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">150</span>年悠久历史的乌克兰国家爱乐“里森科”音乐厅（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">The National Philharmonic of Ukraine --The Lysenko Hall</span>），每年从<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">9</span>月至次年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">6</span>月的演出季大约有<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">60</span>场的定期交响音乐会和数十场的巡演。<br /></span> <span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: medium;">  <img src="http://www.chinacno.org/images/2012/12/yyt/Ukraine/uk-01.png" border="0" width="556" height="371" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: bottom; margin-right: auto;" /></span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">16</span>年来，在首席指挥米科拉<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">.</span>加久拉（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Mikola Diadiura</span>）的调教和乐团音乐家的努力工作下，乐团的国际声誉渐起，被誉为是东欧地区的顶级乐团以及斯拉夫音乐最纯正的演绎团体。作为乌克兰最优秀的交响乐团，乌克兰音乐文化的代表，常年在世界范围内进行巡回演出，其成功的演出音乐会遍及柏林爱乐厅，科隆爱乐厅，东京三得利音乐厅，日内瓦维多利亚音乐厅等世界顶级音乐厅。从<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2001</span>年至<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2009</span>年，连续<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">9</span>年获邀参加全世界最重要交响音乐节之一的法国<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">““La Chaise”-Dieu”</span>音乐节，更在<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2009</span>年作为压轴，与法国童声合唱团，乌克兰歌剧院合唱团，乌克兰<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">“Dumka”</span>合唱团，乌克兰广播合唱团联袂上演马勒第八交响乐，成为当年音乐界一大盛事<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">。<br /></span></span><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><br /><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">    <span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">    </span></span>在</span></span></span>过去的一年里，乐团刚刚成功完成了瑞士，日本和德国的巡回演出，受到以苛刻著称的西欧乐评家的极大好评以及音乐爱好者们的广泛关注。</span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: medium;"> <img src="http://www.chinacno.org/images/2012/12/yyt/Ukraine/uk-02.png" border="0" width="632" height="255" /></span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">德国《科隆新闻》报评论道：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>“彼得·柴可夫斯基第六交响曲……被充满激情，热血、震撼的力量和精湛的演奏技巧表演得如此完美，是为数不多的征服观众的来自东欧的乐团。”</span><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Newspaper “Koelner Stadttanzeiger” wrote, that the performance of Tchaikovskiy’s Sixth Symphony was such a bright one, with such warmth, with the blood of heart, pushful force and instrumental virtuosity that are inherent only just to a few orchestras of East Europe. Audience was charmed.”</span>）</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="Section1" style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">在世界各地的音乐会里，乐团常常与最顶尖的独奏家合作，为观众献上完美的听觉享受，合作过的帕瓦罗提（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Luciano Pavarotti</span>），阿卡多（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Salvatore Accardo</span>），克拉涅夫（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Vladimir Krainev</span>），巴施梅特（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Yuriy Bashmet</span>），古特曼（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Natalia Gutman</span>），克莱默（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Gidon Kremer</span>），吉特里斯（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Ivry Gitlis</span>），神尾真由子，索科洛夫，拉杜罗维奇等音乐大师，他们都对乐团的演奏和配合赞赏不已。</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">乐团在多年的演出和排练中，积累了极广泛的演奏曲目，从古典的莫扎特贝多芬，浪漫风格的勃拉姆斯马勒，无一没有自己独特的演绎风格和音乐表现。对于柴可夫斯基，拉赫玛尼诺夫，肖斯塔科维奇等苏俄派作曲家的作品，更是将其中东斯拉夫民族的热情奔放和宽广浑厚表现得淋漓尽致，纯正的风格，优美的旋律打动了不知多少观众的心，让他们不吝用极其热烈掌声一次次为乐团喝彩。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #050505; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square;">
<li>
<div style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: large;">指挥简介</span></strong></div>
</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;"><strong><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">维塔利<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">·</span>普罗塔索夫</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">这位生于<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1971</span>年，来自乌克兰辛菲罗波尔的新锐指挥，维塔利<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">·</span></span>普罗塔索夫是乌克兰著名的现代派音乐推动者，他创建了乌克兰第一个也是最负盛名的新音乐室内乐团《<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Kiev-Symphonietta</span>》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">。</span>在古典作品演奏领域，师从于指挥大师罗曼<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">.</span>霍夫曼（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Roman.Kofman</span>）的他，将其多年研究新音乐的独特视角融汇到经典作品的演绎中去，形成了他独特的冷静内在且热情奔放的风格。</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #050505; font-size: medium;">维塔利<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">·</span></span>普罗塔索夫作为乌克兰国家爱乐乐团的常任指挥，曾与许多知名的独奏家合作，在<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2011-2012</span>音乐季，他和世界级小提琴家瓦列里<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">·</span></span>索科洛夫与瓦金<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">·</span></span>布罗德斯基合作演奏的小提琴协奏曲系列音乐会受到观众热情欢迎。此外他还多次受邀，作为客席指挥与波恩贝多芬乐团，基辅室内乐团，利沃夫爱乐乐团等知名乐团合作。</span><br /><br /></p>		</div>

		
			
	</div>

</div>
